ee0de","status":"APPROVED","source":"ADMIN","title":"Medici Ballet","location":"Unknown","dateMonth":null,"dateYear":1957,"dateIsUnknown":false,"submitterName":"Admin","messageText":null,"frontImagePath":"/api/images/eee0de52-9c5a-4e3f-ae23-a890f110c084-front.jpg","backImagePath":"/api/images/eee0de52-9c5a-4e3f-ae23-a890f110c084-back.jpg","frontThumbPath":"/api/images/eee0de52-9c5a-4e3f-ae23-a890f110c084-front-thumb.jpg","backThumbPath":"/api/images/eee0de52-9c5a-4e3f-ae23-a890f110c084-back-thumb.jpg","scheduledFor":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-02T21:06:45.383Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-02T21:08:10.987Z"},{"id":"afbff25b-94c9-4d7f-b622-c57aaeecb72f","slug":"london-bridge-london-uk-afbff2","status":"APPROVED","source":"ADMIN","title":"London Bridge","location":"London, UK","dateMonth":null,"dateYear":1902,"dateIsUnknown":false,"submitterName":"Admin","messageText":"Did you write to G. for her 21st birthday? We sent her a silver topped scent bottle from the Pot Cousins (milford & Ballop). You share is 1/6 which you owe to Jess. Can you pay yourself as shall I get you [London] pay no [illegible] let me know.\n\nJust to get to the station I galloped from the bottom of the hill before the station. The train was just going but the guard stopped it after I had nodded my head at the guard. I had an awfully fine time at Milford.\n\nOh! what do you think I went to tea with Daisy the other day. Had an awful scare. Dawks was very shy that [?].\n\nLooked keen in rain. I did not think so!!! Must stop now.\n\nSay said he was very shy that [?].\n\nKindest wishes\nto the\nBid","frontImagePath":"/api/images/afbff25b-94c9-4d7f-b622-c57aaeecb72f-front.jpg","backImagePath":"/api/images/afbff25b-94c9-4d7f-b622-c57aaeecb72f-back.jpg","frontThumbPath":"/api/images/afbff25b-94c9-4d7f-b622-c57aaeecb72f-front-thumb.jpg","backThumbPath":"/api/images/afbff25b-94c9-4d7f-b622-c57aaeecb72f-back-thumb.jpg","scheduledFor":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-02T20:13:03.338Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-02T20:13:45.905Z"},{"id":"ed10bfbf-1eb6-4f47-8e44-fad1bfc86854","slug":"ferhat-pasha-mosque-banja-luka-present-day-bosnia-ed10bf","status":"APPROVED","source":"ADMIN","title":"Ferhat Pasha Mosque","location":"Banja Luka, present day Bosnia","dateMonth":null,"dateYear":1960,"dateIsUnknown":false,"submitterName":"Admin","messageText":"Dear Mum,\n\nWe will probably be at the back and unable to return. Don’t worry about us.\n\nStill have beautiful weather here. Have a flat near the town centre, though there is a climb of 20 steps. Careful walking at night.\n\nDubrovnik is one of the nicest places we have seen. The old town is very good. Food is good and cheap and people are friendly.\n\nHope all is well at home.\n\nLove,\n[?]","frontImagePath":"/api/images/ed10bfbf-1eb6-4f47-8e44-fad1bfc86854-front.jpg","backImagePath":"/api/images/ed10bfbf-1eb6-4f47-8e44-fad1bfc86854-back.jpg","frontThumbPath":"/api/images/ed10bfbf-1eb6-4f47-8e44-fad1bfc86854-front-thumb.jpg","backThumbPath":"/api/images/ed10bfbf-1eb6-4f47-8e44-fad1bfc86854-back-thumb.jpg","scheduledFor":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-02T20:10:15.193Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-02T20:11:28.742Z"},{"id":"2309cdbe-1bc9-4571-ad9a-87e1272fd083","slug":"dubrovnik-dubrovnik-present-day-croatia-2309cd","status":"APPROVED","source":"ADMIN","title":"Dubrovnik","location":"Dubrovnik, present day Croatia","dateMonth":null,"dateYear":1960,"dateIsUnknown":false,"submitterName":"Admin","messageText":"Dear Mum,\n\nWe will probably be at the back and unable to return. Don’t worry about us.\n\nStill have beautiful weather here. Have a flat near the town centre, though there is a climb of 20 steps. Careful walking at night.\n\nDubrovnik is one of the nicest places we have seen. The old town is very good. Food is good and cheap and people are friendly.\n\nHope all is well at home.\n\nLove,\n[?]","frontImagePath":"/api/images/2309cdbe-1bc9-4571-ad9a-87e1272fd083-front.jpg","backImagePath":"/api/images/2309cdbe-1bc9-4571-ad9a-87e1272fd083-back.jpg","frontThumbPath":"/api/images/2309cdbe-1bc9-4571-ad9a-87e1272fd083-front-thumb.jpg","backThumbPath":"/api/images/2309cdbe-1bc9-4571-ad9a-87e1272fd083-back-thumb.jpg","scheduledFor":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-02T20:08:09.064Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-02T20:09:28.870Z"},{"id":"353c5ec1-7068-4d62-902c-1be93d2dfec7","slug":"belfast-belfast-uk-353c5e","status":"APPROVED","source":"ADMIN","title":"Belfast","location":"Belfast, UK","dateMonth":null,"dateYear":1957,"dateIsUnknown":false,"submitterName":"Admin","messageText":"Belfast.\n\nArrived safely late evening. Off on a 3 hour adventure starting at 10.30. Then a slight mishap but all well now.\n\nTime is slipping by very fast. The Grand Central has turned out very good. Today hope you are having a lovely time.\n\nLove,\n[?]","frontImagePath":"/api/images/353c5ec1-7068-4d62-902c-1be93d2dfec7-front.jpg","backImagePath":"/api/images/353c5ec1-7068-4d62-902c-1be93d2dfec7-back.jpg","frontThumbPath":"/api/images/353c5ec1-7068-4d62-902c-1be93d2dfec7-front-thumb.jpg","backThumbPath":"/api/images/353c5ec1-7068-4d62-902c-1be93d2dfec7-back-thumb.jpg","scheduledFor":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-02T20:07:09.738Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-02T20:07:26.324Z"},{"id":"26857d2b-534e-4e55-84f1-7ac73644d55c","slug":"sousse-tunisia-26857d","status":"APPROVED","source":"ADMIN","title":"Sousse","location":"Tunisia","dateMonth":null,"dateYear":1966,"dateIsUnknown":false,"submitterName":"Admin","messageText":"Dear Henry,\n\nAs 10.20 the sun was shining & we had a lovely flight, everything excellent. Big congestion at Tunis airport as many Tunisians were returning from a visit to Mecca.\n\nThe hotel is lovely, bedrooms large. I have a double room. How about coming over for the end of [?], but the place will not be finished until another month.\n\nI do not think the food service will be so very hot. They are still a young country trying to cater for visitors. At the moment there are about 350 here. They would take more.\n\nPrices are high but we were warned about that, so have our own food in. Take care if you do not attempt the ceiling.\n\nLove to Stan","frontImagePath":"/api/images/26857d2b-534e-4e55-84f1-7ac73644d55c-front.jpg","backImagePath":"/api/images/26857d2b-534e-4e55-84f1-7ac73644d55c-back.jpg","frontThumbPath":"/api/images/26857d2b-534e-4e55-84f1-7ac73644d55c-front-thumb.jpg","backThumbPath":"/api/images/26857d2b-534e-4e55-84f1-7ac73644d55c-back-thumb.jpg","scheduledFor":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-02T19:53:36.608Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-02T19:56:27.133Z"},{"id":"2b93d3e7-af5a-4993-8305-eeb527266e6e","slug":"rydal-water-cumbria-uk-2b93d3","status":"APPROVED","source":"ADMIN","title":"Rydal Water","location":"Cumbria, UK","dateMonth":null,"dateYear":1902,"dateIsUnknown":false,"submitterName":"Admin","messageText":"Dear M.,\n\nHope you are having a good time. We are enjoying ourselves here. The weather has been very fine. We have had a nice time walking round Rydal Water.\n\nLove from\n[?]","frontImagePath":"/api/images/2b93d3e7-af5a-4993-8305-eeb527266e6e-front.jpg","backImagePath":"/api/images/2b93d3e7-af5a-4993-8305-eeb527266e6e-back.jpg","frontThumbPath":"/api/images/2b93d3e7-af5a-4993-8305-eeb527266e6e-front-thumb.jpg","backThumbPath":"/api/images/2b93d3e7-af5a-4993-8305-eeb527266e6e-back-thumb.jpg","scheduledFor":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-02T19:53:36.188Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-02T19:57:40.040Z"},{"id":"40558c0d-abf2-467f-a85a-e3ee62456b10","slug":"honfleur-france-40558c","status":"APPROVED","source":"ADMIN","title":"Honfleur","location":"France","dateMonth":null,"dateYear":null,"dateIsUnknown":true,"submitterName":"Admin","messageText":null,"frontImagePath":"/api/images/40558c0d-abf2-467f-a85a-e3ee62456b10-front.jpg","backImagePath":"/api/images/40558c0d-abf2-467f-a85a-e3ee62456b10-back.jpg","frontThumbPath":"/api/images/40558c0d-abf2-467f-a85a-e3ee62456b10-front-thumb.jpg","backThumbPath":"/api/images/40558c0d-abf2-467f-a85a-e3ee62456b10-back-thumb.jpg","scheduledFor":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-02T19:53:35.734Z","updatedAt":"2